{"segment":2,"line_start":91,"line_end":144,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_da_lao_ban","speaker_name":"大老板","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"你看怎么样？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":113,"line_end":113},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_da_lao_ban","text":"看来这九个人都是杀人的好手。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":119,"line_end":119},{"speaker":"char_da_lao_ban","speaker_name":"大老板","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"他们杀的人都不少？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":121,"line_end":123},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_da_lao_ban","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":125,"line_end":125},{"speaker":"char_da_lao_ban","speaker_name":"大老板","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"你看他们能不能对付那个没有用的阿吉？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":127,"line_end":127},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_da_lao_ban","text":"他们有九个人，阿吉只有一双手，他们杀的人也一定比阿吉多！","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":129,"line_end":129},{"speaker":"char_da_lao_ban","speaker_name":"大老板","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"明天一早就叫人分头去接他们，只要他们的人一到，就送到韩大奶奶那里去。","tone":"微笑","chapter":21,"line_start":131,"line_end":131},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_da_lao_ban","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":133,"line_end":133},{"speaker":"char_da_lao_ban","speaker_name":"大老板","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"他们一定是分批来的，这么样九个人聚在一起，太引人注意。","tone":"认真","chapter":21,"line_start":135,"line_end":135},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_da_lao_ban","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":137,"line_end":137},{"speaker":"char_da_lao_ban","speaker_name":"大老板","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"要杀人，就不能引人注意。","tone":"认真","chapter":21,"line_start":139,"line_end":139},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_da_lao_ban","text":"是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":141,"line_end":141},{"speaker":"char_da_lao_ban","speaker_name":"大老板","listener":"cha