","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"我姓杜，杜方！","tone":"认真","chapter":21,"line_start":251,"line_end":251},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_du_fang","text":"黑煞剑杜方？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":253,"line_end":253},{"speaker":"char_du_fang","speaker_name":"杜方","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"我们一向河水不犯井水，你……","tone":"认真","chapter":21,"line_start":255,"line_end":255},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_du_fang","text":"那么你们就不该到这里来。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":257,"line_end":257},{"speaker":"char_du_fang","speaker_name":"杜方","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"难道这件事你们已接了下来？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":259,"line_end":259},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_du_fang","text":"难道我们不能接？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":21,"line_start":261,"line_end":261},{"speaker":"char_du_fang","speaker_name":"杜方","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"我知道只要是黑杀接下的事，就没有人能插手。","tone":"认真","chapter":21,"line_start":263,"line_end":263},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_du_fang","text":"你知道就很好！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":21,"line_start":265,"line_end":265},{"speaker":"char_du_fang","speaker_name":"杜方","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"但是我并不知道你们已插手！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":21,"line_start":267,"line_end":267},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_du_fang","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":269,"line_end":269},{"speaker":"char_du_fang","speaker_name":"杜方","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"所以你一定要杀人。","tone":"认真","chapter":21,"line_start":271,"line_end":271},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_du_fang","text":"一定要杀！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":21,"line_start":273,"line_end":273},{"speaker":"char_du_fang","speaker_name":"杜方","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":275,"line_end":275},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_du_fang","text":"我喜欢杀人！","tone":"冷酷","ch