{"segment":4,"line_start":301,"line_end":383,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"现在你已知道我是谁？","tone":"冷酷","chapter":21,"line_start":307,"line_end":307},{"speaker":"char_chang_san","speaker_name":"长三","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"是。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":21,"line_start":309,"line_end":309},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"你怕我？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":21,"line_start":313,"line_end":313},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"我知道你一定也杀过人，为什么要怕我？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":317,"line_end":317},{"speaker":"char_chang_san","speaker_name":"长三","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"因为……因为……","tone":"恐惧","chapter":21,"line_start":319,"line_end":319},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"是因为我杀人的方法可怕，还是因为我喜欢杀人？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":21,"line_start":321,"line_end":321},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"你见过白木没有？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":327,"line_end":327},{"speaker":"char_chang_san","speaker_name":"长三","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"没有。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":21,"line_start":329,"line_end":329},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"你若能见到他杀人，才会明白要怎样杀人才能真正算杀人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":331,"line_end":331},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"你有没有见过江岛和佐佐木？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":337,"line_end":337},{"speaker":"char_chang_san","speaker_name":"长三","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"没有。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":21,"line_start":339,"line_end":339},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"你若见到他们，才会明白要什么样的人才算喜欢杀人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":341,"line_end":341},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"我杀人至少还有原因，他们杀人却只不过是为了自己高兴。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":345,"line_end":345},{"speaker":"char_chang_san","speaker_name":"长三","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"只要他们高兴，随时都会杀人？","tone":"恐惧","chapter":21,"line_start":347,"line_end":347},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"随时随地，随便什么人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":349,"line_end":349},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"你知不知道血是什么味道？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":21,"line_start":361,"line_end":361},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"你只要尝一尝，就会知道了。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":21,"line_start":365,"line_end":365},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_chang_san","text":"难道大老板手下，都是你这种连血都不敢尝的脓包？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":21,"line_start":369,"line_end":369},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"不是的。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":371,"line_end":371},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"你也是大老板的手下？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":379,"line_end":379},{"speaker":"char_xiao_di","speaker_name":"小弟","listener":"char_hei_gui","text":"我也是，我叫小弟。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":381,"line_end":381},{"speaker":"char_hei_gui","speaker_name":"黑鬼","listener":"char_xiao_di","text":"你尝过血是什么味道？","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":21,"line_start":383,"line_end":383}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_bai_mu","name":"白木","alias":[],"identity":"武当弟子，被逐出门墙后仍着道装","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"武当弟子被逐出门墙后仍着道装，佩剑六尺八寸，面黄体瘦，眉角有痣","personality":{"traits":["冷酷","精准","狠辣","沉着","孤傲"],"speech_style":"冷酷","temperament":"冷酷"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[21],"source_refs":[{"chapter":21,"line_start":93,"line_end":93,"text":"白木。武当弟子，被逐出门墙后仍着道装"}]},{"id":"char_tu_he_shang","name":"土和尚","alias":[],"identity":"出身少林的头陀","faction":null,"r